{"tid":1478302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一手國泰香港人加油","createTime":"2019-08-16T12:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T13:18:13.000Z","uid":284195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"480c09981853a539638b17ba6d8093df5ed893ba","tid":1478302,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>一人買一手國泰， 麻煩廢中出場<br />\n<br />\n0293 ，一手10k <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"c7fa02f491483e3ca588388217a4ef0f2985cc3c","tid":1478302,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/uz68KJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuz68KJX.png&h=a0c87415&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5806f89924d6d5416b12ab3cb6d6b49196f63f97","tid":1478302,"uid":195655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"咁多股東係中資，點解要幫佢托市"},{"pid":"f6d8878ecbc40e9aab0c3728d4ff8784b495a763","tid":1478302,"uid":194745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:42:23.000Z","msg":"國泰不嬲好嘅只係啲機師空姐，國泰航空間公司同管理層不嬲對機師空姐極差，只因有機師空姐工會幫佢哋。啲管理層只是吸血蛀米大蟲，吸盡機師同空姐的工作成果。<br />\n<br />\n啲管理層炒燃油對沖蝕錢，就搵員工裁員找數。自己亂駛錢大花筒就刻薄空姐，減航班人手加座位。<br />\n<br />\n大家要分開公司同員工，pacific place啲員工幫手，唔代表太古幫手。太古不嬲都是奶共㗎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">啲管理層已經將員工名單交給民航局，嗰啲示威表過態嘅黃絲空姐機師冇得飛越中國領空，好快會被迫走，成間公司上上下下管理層機師空姐都會係藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n太古一早已經奶共，當初自願將國泰股權交出媚共自保，繼續揾銀。反而怡和遷冊撤出香港。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F86420&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0TcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=a6b474c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新CEO 黃生來自港機工程，一早紮根厦門，一定好識做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n去台灣，長榮/中華<br />\n<br />\n去日本， JAL ANA PEACH<br />\n<br />\n去歐洲 英航，三寶, virgin Air France lufthansa<br />\n<br />\n去澳洲 virgin qantas<br />\n<br />\n去美國 AA United<br />\n<br />\n去中國  冇計 國泰港龍"},{"pid":"ae5baa631a8e19c4c5e9a45fd5d7fd572dbf3b92","tid":1478302,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"唔想香港的航空公司孌了大陸公司😌😌😌"},{"pid":"3519267daecf5201e4fbb6bfd373c5f86deef7bd","tid":1478302,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae5baa631a8e19c4c5e9a45fd5d7fd572dbf3b92","tid":1478302,"uid":284195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"唔想香港的航空公司孌了大陸公司😌😌😌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}